            <bug_when>2008-08-01 11:52:51 +0000</bug_when>
            <thetext>This is not a bug, but a feature. OpenGrok will just search for files containing the definition, but it will list all occurrences of the symbol in the files that contain the definition. If you look in the search result it will print &quot;function&quot; behind the mach for the actual definition in the file.

If you dislike this behavior, please reopen the issue and create a patch that removes the other results :-)</thetext>
